@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
title D2: Normal Request Flow — 5 Phases of Active Replication\n(Kaashoek's Variant, No Faults)

actor "Client" as C
participant "FE\n(Student 1)" as FE #E3F2FD
participant "Sequencer\n(Student 3)" as SEQ #FFF8E1
participant "Replica 1" as R1 #E8F5E9
participant "Replica 2" as R2 #E8F5E9
participant "Replica 3" as R3 #E8F5E9
participant "Replica 4" as R4 #E8F5E9

== Phase 1: Request ==

C -> FE : SOAP: reserveVehicle(\nMTLU1111, MTL1001,\n01032026, 10032026)
activate FE
FE -> FE : Generate unique requestID

FE -> SEQ : UDP REQUEST:\nreqID, feHost, fePort,\noperation, params
activate SEQ
SEQ --> FE : ACK

== Phase 2: Coordination (Total Order via Sequencer) ==

SEQ -> SEQ : s_g = sequenceCounter++\nStore in historyBuffer[s_g]

SEQ -> R1 : EXECUTE: s_g, reqID,\nfeHost, fePort, op, params
SEQ -> R2 : EXECUTE: s_g, reqID,\nfeHost, fePort, op, params
SEQ -> R3 : EXECUTE: s_g, reqID,\nfeHost, fePort, op, params
SEQ -> R4 : EXECUTE: s_g, reqID,\nfeHost, fePort, op, params
deactivate SEQ

R1 --> SEQ : ACK
R2 --> SEQ : ACK
R3 --> SEQ : ACK
R4 --> SEQ : ACK

== Phase 3: Execution (State Machine — same order, same result) ==

R1 -> R1 : s_g == r_g?\nYes: execute via\nVehicleReservationWS\nr_g++
R2 -> R2 : Execute (same order)
R3 -> R3 : Execute (same order)
R4 -> R4 : Execute (same order)

== Phase 4: Agreement (none needed — total order guarantees) ==

note over R1, R4 : No agreement phase needed.\nSequencer total order ensures identical execution.

== Phase 5: Response (FE Voting: f+1 = 2 identical) ==

R1 -> FE : RESULT: s_g, reqID, R1,\n"SUCCESS: Reserved MTL1001.\nCost: 80.0 Remaining: 920.0"
R2 -> FE : RESULT: s_g, reqID, R2,\n"SUCCESS: Reserved MTL1001.\nCost: 80.0 Remaining: 920.0"

note over FE #E3F2FD
  **2 identical results received (f+1=2)**
  Return to client immediately
end note

FE --> C : "SUCCESS: Reserved MTL1001.\nCost: 80.0 Remaining budget: 920.0"
deactivate FE

R3 -> FE : RESULT (same — late)
R4 -> FE : RESULT (same — late)
note over FE : All 4 match: byzantineCount\nreset to 0 for all replicas
@enduml
